{"tid":1583773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世]邊個再負面文宣我立即屌你老母","createTime":"2019-09-20T19:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T08:57:19.000Z","uid":149161,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"07d537324851d0b066f84027994541de72b1810b","tid":1583773,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:04:51.000Z","msg":"喂大佬 你想引起人注意就講下理據 <br />\n屌你老母乜柒運動玩撚完 乜乜活動上唔到熱門 乜乜無人講 <br />\n咁撚負面 睇得多情緒都唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n點解依家有少部份手足頂唔順自殺某程度係因為佢哋對負面嘅嘢敏感 <br />\n佢哋見到你哋嘅負面文宣只會灰而唔會走入嚟睇 <br />\n<br />\n至於點做文宣 個人覺得日程表就夠 清晰簡單直接 依方面我冇乜意見 <br />\n但係總之邊個再負面文宣我真係屌你老母 煩到閪咁 認同嘅幫推同正皮 屌 講完"},{"pid":"3966f0b9f33f652f3254ccec5be50e6544198d30","tid":1583773,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:05:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"5c6dc689556781684647386f01b726d2fb8d6e52","tid":1583773,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8197e927adadf502db7028c87b63f68fea633b","tid":1583773,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626d5249a6dc378e7e0282c816a15009b80792c9","tid":1583773,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de9c3acd4a1ad0a9877996a4a8f8fa9721e140d","tid":1583773,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p