連登勿認真」，內容可認真睇，但連登仔講嘢態度真係唔好咁上心，佢哋落心落力去出力做嘢，但上到嚟俾人屌，佢真係會無名火氣，甚至問我係咪對家打嘅嘢玩分化"},{"pid":"ca8a117ed3141c27a5355573b729287df12c1f91","tid":1583773,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8714f9b43e6f2f4fb0bcab31d568cf04b8000650","tid":1583773,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:00:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9a7afe98168ce478fcbafce3affd0558044d419","tid":1583773,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc0db05a0e6fa51abdb786484d2962f70cd376a","tid":1583773,"uid":105032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a29ed05e9a23d9367f34b93c5f4391897bcc0ac","tid":1583773,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"又要返去佔中快樂抗爭？<br />\n5年前未柒夠？<br />\nMentality夠強就自然頂得順唔會自殺㗎啦<br />\n要死都會攬埋警察一齊死"},{"pid":"c848bc79a5d8822cc88809919ed98c303f6903c9","tid":1583773,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b9c391f5dbf031f6b5a85349bc0b83af0ebd46a","tid":1583773,"uid":192699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GDS9aL7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGDS9aL7.jpg&h=9db72a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都係文宣組，入嚟拎圖印<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 